{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slap-It Together! is a silly, first-person slapper (yes, slapper) where you must fight off waves of enemies to escape a gameshow. <i>Plants vs Zombies</i> meets <i>Left 4 Dead</i>\u00a0in this fun, physics sandbox. Play in singleplayer or with up to 4 friends in online co-op!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520590/extras/Multiplayer.gif?t=1738854234\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get your brain churning (the zombies love it!) and figure out the various brain-teasers to progress through the various levels at your disposal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520590/extras/PuzzleTunnel.gif?t=1738854234\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVE THE HORDES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These brain-dead buffoons will stop at nothing to entertain the audience, even if it means making a fool out of you. <strong>Stop them!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520590/extras/ClobberFoes.gif?t=1738854234\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ESCAPE THE SHOW!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have been kidnapped and forced to participate in this zany spectacle, but don't let that dampen your spirits!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <i>Slap-It Games</i> are sure to make someone smile...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520590/extras/Elevator_Tease_600px.gif?t=1738854234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you play along with Dr. Rio Rascal's maniacal game and hope for the best, or will you put your foot down and give the audience a show they'll never forget? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The choice is yours, but choose wisely, or you might end up as the punchline of the next joke.  </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Learn the Ropes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/cb297b3b0cdc9979dccb8b26d2833f650be7b8fa.jpg"},{"name":"Basic Zombie Slapper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/ee60b82090183189189bf1b818bae5fba1f91a65.jpg"},{"name":"Advanced Zombie Slapper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/267f2156ca8707a7ac67bd08cc8a59220fa478f6.jpg"},{"name":"Professional Zombie Slapper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/178eee7c842e0bdd4cc79449f66d064dabdf8862.jpg"},{"name":"Expert Zombie Slapper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/9703c127d601c5a70793751c86087de3fe9bb721.jpg"},{"name":"Winner Winner Chicken Dinner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/9d540d01cc6ac4e29614870af1694164ea982d3b.jpg"},{"name":"Rooftops Rejoice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/8a9684eddb0b04f500534392850d6b37b6247804.jpg"},{"name":"Twisted Tunnels","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/6586bd9edd55bd36fb8331c1f58f42052080bf82.jpg"},{"name":"Armed and Ready","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/fe1d42c610196a5f1ae19dd1cc491c00c2d2e1f2.jpg"},{"name":"Is it play-time yet?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1520590/b2fdbad4cd3445c62f93350ffc0adb85d7c958bb.jpg"}],"total":18},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738854234","background_raw":"https://shar